reviewText: Its ok, not worth the price

The reason for giving this item 2 stars rating based on this instructional video was not gear towards individual who have never perform the task of completely done hair weaving. I purchased this item to have understanding of learning to do my own hair weaving but I was mislead.  This item is gear towards personal who have done or at least attempt of weaving hair. The difficulties I have experience with this item was the lack of how to accomplish the task of weaving and different ways of braiding the hair into patterns. I was totally confused and disappointed especially when I waited for weeks to receive such item.
I enjoy watching this video and I did my first sew in on my daughter. It did not turn out bad. I feel this will help me better my skills to do sew ins.
Its ok, when in dought i refer to this book to help me with braiding and cutting, I will continue to by  more for my shop and for my educational pleasure
Love the video, great detail, easy to follow everyone loved my new hair doo. yea. i did it my self.....thanks to the teacher.
